      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>UNOWITZ - Bernard (Bernie), peacefully on July 13, 2000. Cherished husband of Debra, devoted father of Rose Unowitz and Nancy Muller. Loving grandfather of Emily and Brian Muller. His extraordinary kindness and warmth will never be forgotten. Graveside service Sunday, July 16, 11 AM at Sharon Gardens, Valhalla, NY. For information, call ''Wein &amp; Wein'' 800-322-0533.</p>
      </block>
